254
00:49:15.736 --> 00:49:19.736
If you make it. it will be the same way
you made it here.

255
00:49:20.117 --> 00:49:23.112
You have to break your way out.

256
00:49:25.404 --> 00:49:30.177
You should be careful.
You're not here to do good.

257
00:49:30.633 --> 00:49:34.094
Don't be blind. I've seen that old
man here before.

258
00:49:34.615 --> 00:49:37.615
He knows this building as well as I do..

259
00:49:39.420 --> 00:49:41.475
Not every cop is swayed by money sir.

260
00:49:41.474 --> 00:49:44.874
If I believed that I would never
have opened the door.

261
00:49:58.839 --> 00:50:00.839
He's bone headed and stubborn

262
00:50:01.975 --> 00:50:03.975
But he's a good man.

263
00:50:04.821 --> 00:50:07.621
Take care of him.
I'll be back as soon as I can.

264
00:50:20.806 --> 00:50:23.606
<i>Spare me. please!</i>

265
00:50:44.983 --> 00:50:47.483
Man that's too much!

266
00:50:52.769 --> 00:50:54.769
He's here!

267
00:51:23.912 --> 00:51:25.912
Up!

268
00:52:44.639 --> 00:52:46.639
Take the leg!

269
00:55:51.298 --> 00:55:53.298
Where'd he come from?

270
00:57:00.428 --> 00:57:02.728
Stop it! Calm down!

271
00:57:07.922 --> 00:57:11.316
What the fuck are you doing here?

272
00:57:22.508 --> 00:57:24.302
Keep on watching

273
00:57:45.631 --> 00:57:47.631
They're gone.

274
00:57:49.243 --> 00:57:51.243
We don't know that yet.

275
00:57:52.961 --> 00:57:57.961
Think about it Jaka. one's a cripple
the other a rookie.

276
00:57:58.322 --> 00:58:00.322
They didn't stand a chance.

277
00:58:00.936 --> 00:58:04.936
Now I'm sorry. but we're not going up
there just to find their dead bodies.

278
00:58:08.943 --> 00:58:10.986
Listen to me you prick.

279
00:58:11.037 --> 00:58:14.533
When it comes to the lives of my men
it would be wise for you to shut the fuck up.

280
00:58:15.445 --> 00:58:17.445
You wanna talk about risking lives?!

281
00:58:17.955 --> 00:58:20.651
Well you already risked theirs.

282
00:58:21.097 --> 00:58:23.097
And now I own yours.

283
00:58:23.557 --> 00:58:26.057
Who ordered this?
-- What?

284
00:58:26.522 --> 00:58:28.616
Well it sure as shit wasn't you.

285
00:58:28.616 --> 00:58:32.016
No one leads the charge when it comes
to their own dirty work.

286
00:58:33.875 --> 00:58:35.875
Careful Jaka.

287
00:58:36.199 --> 00:58:39.183
Remember your rank.
-- Rank?

288
00:58:39.181 --> 00:58:42.775
Rank counts for shit now.
Once we make it out of here..

289
00:58:43.238 --> 00:58:47.738
You'll be mopping up puddles of piss
in a prison cell for the rest of your life.

290
00:58:48.593 --> 00:58:51.093
We're not here to do good.

291
00:58:52.110 --> 00:58:55.404
We're here to make someone rich.

292
00:58:55.740 --> 00:58:59.734
I'm asking you one last time.
Who ordered the hit?

293
00:59:02.379 --> 00:59:07.173
Another time maybe. I'll take my
chances here first.

294
00:59:11.658 --> 00:59:13.658
Suit yourself.

295
00:59:15.623 --> 00:59:20.115
We're going back up there.
We're going to find them.

296
00:59:20.892 --> 00:59:22.892
And only then do we leave.

297
00:59:25.058 --> 00:59:27.367
Any objections?

298
00:59:29.602 --> 00:59:31.602
Thought not.

299
00:59:32.628 --> 00:59:34.628
Everyone ready.

300
00:59:37.091 --> 00:59:39.486
Move.

301
01:00:03.957 --> 01:00:06.453
Protect him! Now!!

302
01:01:35.674 --> 01:01:38.668
I've never really liked using these.

303
01:01:41.607 --> 01:01:45.600
Takes away the rush.

304
01:01:46.497 --> 01:01:51.154
Squeezing a trigger....
... it's like ordering takeout.

305
01:01:52.196 --> 01:01:54.196
Now this ...

306
01:01:55.847 --> 01:01:58.241
This is the thing.

307
01:01:59.189 --> 01:02:02.683
This is the pulse.

308
01:02:03.554 --> 01:02:06.054
This is what I do.

309
01:05:05.434 --> 01:05:07.434
You shouldn't be here.

310
01:05:10.112 --> 01:05:13.606
Nor should you.

311
01:05:18.064 --> 01:05:20.064
Who are they?

312
01:05:25.427 --> 01:05:29.420
they're no one.

313
01:05:33.066 --> 01:05:35.666
Don't they check for any links
before they send you.

314
01:05:35.663 --> 01:05:39.789
They got nothing on record about you.
just your first name.

315
01:05:40.136 --> 01:05:42.436
No one knows shit about us.

316
01:05:44.904 --> 01:05:48.304
I almost fucking choked when they
pinned your photo on the board.

317
01:05:48.379 --> 01:05:51.579
Six years with no contact.
and this is how I find you.

318
01:05:57.470 --> 01:05:59.470
You have to leave this place.

319
01:06:00.977 --> 01:06:04.674
Now.
-- I can't.

320
01:06:04.826 --> 01:06:08.570
Not without my team.
-- What? -- You heard me.

321
01:06:09.234 --> 01:06:11.428
I don't think you realize the
situation you're in.

322
01:06:11.427 --> 01:06:15.027
Oh I understand fine. I'm not the
one living here.

323
01:06:16.350 --> 01:06:21.146
Don't worry about me I'm fine.
Next time you want to talk. just pick up the phone.

324
01:06:21.256 --> 01:06:23.756
I spent the last 24 hours listening to

325
01:06:23.755 --> 01:06:25.855
my best friends to talking about
killing you.

326
01:06:25.930 --> 01:06:27.930
I'm the only one who can get you
out here safely.

327
01:06:28.176 --> 01:06:30.421
And without a pair of fuckin' handcuffs
wrapped around your wrists.

328
01:06:30.520 --> 01:06:34.024
Wait! What's that?
You're getting me out?!

329
01:06:34.099 --> 01:06:36.197
You're the one who needs saving.

330
01:06:36.196 --> 01:06:38.196
Last I checked my guys are almost done
collecting the bodies.

331
01:06:38.252 --> 01:06:42.049
Fuck you Just do what I say.
-- And go where? Home?

332
01:06:43.305 --> 01:06:46.227
If I was such a disappointment to him then...

333
01:06:49.076 --> 01:06:52.735
Think how proud he's gonna be
now that I am who I am.

334
01:06:54.615 --> 01:06:58.913
He just wants you home. we all do.

335
01:07:04.248 --> 01:07:07.197
You don't get it!!

336
01:07:08.407 --> 01:07:11.780
That ain't me anymore. This is.

337
01:07:12.480 --> 01:07:15.280
Just cos you see what I do as wrong.

338
01:07:15.277 --> 01:07:17.277
doesn't mean I can not be good at it.

339
01:07:17.372 --> 01:07:19.372
This is the only thing I know how to do.

340
01:07:19.393 --> 01:07:21.393
I fucking own it.

341
01:07:22.351 --> 01:07:24.351
No. Rama.

342
01:07:25.362 --> 01:07:28.158
I won't go back to who I was.

343
01:07:40.029 --> 01:07:43.423
You're going to be an uncle.

344
01:07:45.727 --> 01:07:48.024
What?

345
01:07:48.807 --> 01:07:51.707
Yes. a boy. due in two months.

346
01:07:59.943 --> 01:08:04.543
You tell me this now...
cos you expect me to leave...?

347
01:08:04.597 --> 01:08:08.097
I told you cos you're my fucking brother.
-- Think about what you're doing!

348
01:08:08.259 --> 01:08:11.656
If you stay here you'll be fucking dead
before that boy is born.

349
01:08:11.736 --> 01:08:15.133
Haven't you thought about that?
-- I've thought about it every day

350
01:08:15.182 --> 01:08:18.379
since I was given this assignment.
And it fucking terrifies me.

351
01:08:21.177 --> 01:08:23.177
This is fucking ridiculous!

352
01:08:31.075 --> 01:08:33.675
You should leave. I don't have much time.

353
01:08:34.284 --> 01:08:37.184
At least change your clothing before
you go back out there.

354
01:08:39.208 --> 01:08:41.808
No. this fits me just fine.

355
01:08:49.604 --> 01:08:56.201
Hang back. til the area is clear.

356
01:09:15.617 --> 01:09:18.217
Wait! Hold the lift.

357
01:09:29.143 --> 01:09:33.026
Where are your men?
-- Still hunting. And yours?

358
01:09:33.297 --> 01:09:35.297
Same.

359
01:09:36.749 --> 01:09:39.149
Where are you taking him?
--  The Boss.

360
01:09:49.579 --> 01:09:51.779
That's not the guy.

361
01:09:51.778 --> 01:09:54.643
It is.
-- No. it definitely isn't.

362
01:09:55.187 --> 01:09:57.187
Plus this guy is dead already.

363
01:09:57.612 --> 01:10:00.012
Yeah well I'm taking him anyway

364
01:10:00.560 --> 01:10:03.160
What have you got?

365
01:10:57.948 --> 01:11:01.140
Rama. Get in.

366
01:11:09.441 --> 01:11:13.234
Where's Bowo?
-- He's safe.

367
01:11:14.293 --> 01:11:18.293
We lost the Sergeant.
-- They got him. he's dead.

368
01:11:20.273 --> 01:11:23.973
Motherfucker dragged him
across the floor like an animal

369
01:11:24.362 --> 01:11:27.762
What happened? Why did you split up?

370
01:11:28.205 --> 01:11:31.405
We were ambushed. outnumbered.

371
01:11:31.461 --> 01:11:36.553
And he ran.
Sergeant ordered me to protect him.

372
01:11:38.581 --> 01:11:42.769
Right now all can do is
try to survive this..

373
01:11:43.072 --> 01:11:45.261
We have to move soon and fast.

374
01:11:45.345 --> 01:11:48.741
You've been the cause of every drop of
blood spilt in this place.

375
01:11:48.878 --> 01:11:51.773
But not now. Now you're gonna
be with us step for step.

376
01:11:51.786 --> 01:11:55.775
Blow for blow. Until this nightmare is over.

377
01:11:56.946 --> 01:12:00.597
Then what?
-- We go up. we attack.

378
01:12:00.726 --> 01:12:05.019
We get who we came here for and
and we use him to get out.

379
01:12:06.147 --> 01:12:10.143
Finding him won't be easy.
-- 15th floor.

380
01:12:10.174 --> 01:12:12.174
It's where he runs everything.

381
01:12:14.382 --> 01:12:16.382
But reaching him is another thing entirely.

382
01:12:16.837 --> 01:12:20.629
And assuming we do get him...
What then? What's your plan?

383
01:12:20.645 --> 01:12:23.669
We'll convince him.
-- How?

384
01:12:23.896 --> 01:12:26.381
All men change with the touch of
a gun barrel to the head.

385
01:12:26.435 --> 01:12:29.430
We don't have a gun. -- Then a knife.
a chair leg. your bare hands. anything.

386
01:12:29.866 --> 01:12:31.963
Just do whatever it takes to
make him ours.

387
01:12:32.063 --> 01:12:35.051
We still have time.
we can still get out.

388
01:12:40.041 --> 01:12:44.029
Who the fuck is that?
-- I told him it's the wrong guy.

389
01:12:45.722 --> 01:12:50.614
He wearing a vest. he counts.
I'm not the one who came back empty handed.

390
01:12:51.234 --> 01:12:54.222
That's not true. is it Andi?

391
01:12:54.493 --> 01:12:56.573
Excuse me.

392
01:12:58.557 --> 01:13:02.446
Surely you've got something to show.

393
01:13:03.522 --> 01:13:08.019
You of all people wouldn't waste
my fucking time for nothing.

394
01:13:08.737 --> 01:13:11.033
I'm sorry. I don't.

395
01:13:13.546 --> 01:13:15.546
Show me your hands.

396
01:13:19.393 --> 01:13:22.385
Bring them here.
-- What? -- here.

397
01:13:34.221 --> 01:13:36.221
Empty.

398
01:13:36.651 --> 01:13:40.148
But I am sure that
you got something. Turn them.

399
01:13:51.413 --> 01:13:55.436
I was wrong.
You did waste my fucking time.

400
01:13:59.275 --> 01:14:03.279
I have found dead bodies. there's a lot of them.
-- Oh Yeah? What else?

401
01:14:03.872 --> 01:14:06.872
If I had to guess. I'd say there are
2 more cops out there.

402
01:14:08.237 --> 01:14:11.137
What if I said there are 3 cops left.
would you agree?

403
01:14:11.139 --> 01:14:15.934
As I said there's a lot of floors.
you could give or take......

404
01:14:16.706 --> 01:14:19.106
Give or take....

405
01:14:27.944 --> 01:14:29.944
You little prick...

406
01:14:29.994 --> 01:14:33.793
I'll admit it I was impressed.
I really was.

407
01:14:34.133 --> 01:14:37.832
But never underestimate the persistence
of paranoia

408
01:14:42.125 --> 01:14:44.124
After seeing that. I'd have sat still
with shit in my pants.

409
01:14:45.568 --> 01:14:49.266
Seems these monitors are the only
truth I got left.

410
01:14:50.748 --> 01:14:54.648
Looks like only this monitor that
I can trust. asshole!

411
01:14:56.242 --> 01:15:00.641
They never lie. they tell me everything
I need to know.

412
01:15:01.430 --> 01:15:03.829
But there's one thing
I wanted to ask.

413
01:15:04.291 --> 01:15:06.291
Why?

414
01:15:06.984 --> 01:15:08.984
Ballsy move like that...

415
01:15:11.863 --> 01:15:14.962
ain't from no clash of conscience.

416
01:15:15.564 --> 01:15:18.164
No there's more to this.

417
01:15:18.881 --> 01:15:22.281
But then I think. "It doesn't matter". cos
you're going to die soon anyway.

418
01:15:22.871 --> 01:15:24.871
I don't really give a shit
about "Why?"anymore.

419
01:15:26.693 --> 01:15:28.693
No. what I want to know is ...

420
01:15:28.812 --> 01:15:33.812
Who is this little cunt that's been tearing
my place up?

421
01:15:35.107 --> 01:15:37.107
And what would it mean for you...

422
01:15:39.549 --> 01:15:44.548
if you were to die infront of him.

423
01:15:45.508 --> 01:15:48.408
Or better yet. for him to be cut open
in front of you!!

424
01:15:50.949 --> 01:15:53.848
Fuck you!

425
01:16:08.415 --> 01:16:12.214
Hurry!

426
01:23:33.826 --> 01:23:36.625
Don't move!
Drop the gun!

427
01:23:40.354 --> 01:23:42.854
Are we gonna play this game now?

428
01:23:43.263 --> 01:23:44.763
Get over here!

429
01:23:45.727 --> 01:23:47.727
Faster!

430
01:23:49.325 --> 01:23:52.025
Did I do something wrong officer?

431
01:23:52.116 --> 01:23:54.616
Shut the fuck up! Put your hands
in the air!

432
01:23:59.040 --> 01:24:01.040
Dagu. tie him!

433
01:24:20.815 --> 01:24:23.015
Now you're going to get me the fuck out of here.

434
01:24:28.805 --> 01:24:31.305
Amazing.

435
01:30:01.991 --> 01:30:05.190
What the hell are you doing? Dagu!

436
01:30:05.345 --> 01:30:07.345
He didn't make it.

437
01:30:07.559 --> 01:30:10.559
Fuck. you motherfucker! Why?

438
01:30:10.943 --> 01:30:13.943
Save it. We're almost done here.

439
01:30:14.127 --> 01:30:16.827
Just one last thing to clean up.

440
01:30:17.452 --> 01:30:19.252
You'll never get out of here.
-- Shut up!

441
01:30:19.424 --> 01:30:22.424
Did you honestly think that it would
be so easy to get in?

442
01:30:22.780 --> 01:30:24.780
Did you think we were that fucking stupid?

443
01:30:25.208 --> 01:30:28.208
I was waiting for you. We all were.

444
01:30:28.474 --> 01:30:30.474
Ready to pick you off one by one.

445
01:30:30.852 --> 01:30:33.452
Didn't work too well did it?

446
01:30:33.518 --> 01:30:39.018
oh I don't know. You got at least 18 dead.

447
01:30:39.094 --> 01:30:40.594
No transportation.

448
01:30:40.903 --> 01:30:43.303
You're stuck here.

449
01:30:46.527 --> 01:30:49.526
You got no-one left.

450
01:30:50.894 --> 01:30:52.894
And if we're talking strength in numbers.

451
01:30:53.165 --> 01:30:57.165
We're talking a bullet.
and I only need one for your fucking head.

452
01:30:58.332 --> 01:31:00.832
You don't get it.
You're already dead.

453
01:31:01.859 --> 01:31:04.359
You're dead since I got the call from Reza.

454
01:31:07.893 --> 01:31:11.893
Now I've got your attention.
It was the name right?

455
01:31:13.225 --> 01:31:17.225
Reza and the rest of the suits have
been happy with me since day one.

456
01:31:20.483 --> 01:31:24.872
Cos I know who to pay
and more importantly. how much.

457
01:31:25.106 --> 01:31:28.746
But you?
All you are is a collector

458
01:31:29.053 --> 01:31:32.051
It was never about replacing me.

459
01:31:32.048 --> 01:31:35.748
They sent you here to die.

460
01:31:37.252 --> 01:31:41.712
Fuck you!
-- No. fuck you. big fucking man!

461
01:31:41.866 --> 01:31:45.666
You listen to me. you think they'll allow you
to join them at the top.

462
01:31:45.726 --> 01:31:49.226
Never! you'll always be looking up.

463
01:31:49.887 --> 01:31:54.287
You think when all this is over they'll
welcome you back and promote you.

464
01:31:54.465 --> 01:31:57.897
Make you a hero?
Never! You fuck!

465
01:31:58.049 --> 01:32:00.848
You'll be met by someone emptying a gun
into your head.

466
01:32:00.846 --> 01:32:04.846
A fucking pillow over
your face while you sleep.

467
01:32:05.490 --> 01:32:08.989
You're Done. you're out.

468
01:32:10.777 --> 01:32:12.777
Asshole

469
01:32:13.672 --> 01:32:16.471
Be quiet.

470
01:33:29.368 --> 01:33:32.868
<i>All residents please return to your rooms.</i>

471
01:33:34.539 --> 01:33:36.939
<i>It's all over.</i>

472
01:33:44.008 --> 01:33:47.507
He always knew that someday someone
would try to fuck him over.

473
01:33:47.534 --> 01:33:49.614
This was his insurance.

474
01:33:49.613 --> 01:33:52.513
It's evidence of every dirty cop
he ever dealt with.

475
01:33:53.825 --> 01:33:56.625
Not everyone you salute is rotten.

476
01:33:56.779 --> 01:33:58.779
Find Bunawar.

477
01:33:58.825 --> 01:34:00.825
He's a good man.

478
01:34:33.189 --> 01:34:35.189
Open the gate!

479
01:34:39.162 --> 01:34:41.162
Just keep walking.

480
01:34:41.266 --> 01:34:43.266
Follow me.

481
01:34:44.557 --> 01:34:47.957
If there's one thing
I know for sure. it's that in this world.

482
01:34:49.417 --> 01:34:51.417
I can protect you.

483
01:34:52.222 --> 01:34:55.622
But can you do the same
for me in yours?

484
01:34:57.095 --> 01:35:02.393
They'll come here.
They'll tear this place to the ground

485
01:35:02.587 --> 01:35:05.786
We'll be long gone before they get here.

486
01:35:08.338 --> 01:35:10.338
Then why stay?

487
01:35:10.436 --> 01:35:13.136
For the same reason you
stayed in that uniform.

488
01:35:15.336 --> 01:35:17.336
It just fits.

489
